      • pure

        @Deprecated
public static PureBigraphFactory pure()
        Deprecated.
        Create a pure bigraph factory with default types for the control's label (StringTypedName) and arity (FiniteOrdinal).

        Note that it is advised to use the respective builder methods (e.g., pureBuilder(AbstractEcoreSignature)) for spawning the required builder classes (e.g., signatures, bigraphs, etc.). This ensures correct management of the internal Ecore metamodel usage. Otherwise, the user has to take care about re-using the generated bigraphical metamodel over a signature with other builders when referring to the same signature.

        Returns:
        a pure bigraph factory
